org.smartclean.service

Class SCSDKMasterService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smartclean.service.SCSDKMasterService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DeviceMgmtSDKInterface, GridsSDKInterface, MetricsSDKInterface, SCSDKClientInterface, SCTeamsPropSDKInterface, WFMSDKInterface

    public class SCSDKMasterService
extends Object
implements SCSDKClientInterface
    This class implements the master interface of the SDK. It reads the sdk config and instantiates the beans of the required modules into app memory.

    • Constructor Detail

      • SCSDKMasterService

        public SCSDKMasterService()
        constructor to initialize the SCSDKMasterService. Initially looks for environment variables; if required environment variables are not found Or environment variables redirects back to sdk config file, the sdk tries to load with the config file. Internally initializes the CredentialManager with 'staleCacheThreshold' set to 15 minutes by default and cacheCleanupFrequency of 10 minutes by default.
